      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 626: Initializing on Status::TRYING marks conversationsInitialized\u003dtrue before the account is fully registered. If the daemon only exposes the deferred conversation list once registration completes, the REGISTERED transition will be skipped and conversations may remain missing. Prefer triggering this one-shot refresh on REGISTERED only, or set conversationsInitialized only after a successful refresh signal/result if initConversations() is asynchronous. Suggested fix:\\n```suggestion\\n            if (status \u003d\u003d api::account::Status::REGISTERED \u0026\u0026 !accountInfo.conversationsInitialized) {\\n                accountInfo.contactModel-\u003einitContacts();\\n                accountInfo.conversationModel-\u003einitConversations();\\n                accountInfo.conversationsInitialized \u003d true;\\n            }\\n```",
